{{Cleanup|date=January 2007}}

'''''Burned Down the Enemy''''' is the third album of [[Heavy metal music|heavy metal]] band [[Burning Point]].  Album released in [[Asia]] by [[Soundholic]] [[20 December]], 2006 and in [[Europe]] 19th of January by [[Metal Heaven]].

It was recorded at Helgate studios in [[Oulu]] by [[Jukka Jokikokko]]. Mixing was made in [[Tonebox]] studios by [[Kakke V<U+00E4>h<U+00E4>kuopus]]. Album was mastered in [[Finnvox]] studios by [[Minerva Pappi]]. 

